snippet.title: ZWAARD - Official kickstarter trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a world where you try to preserve the still existing life forms. Technology has taken over and will try it's best to stop you in your adventure. Whilst those technologies try to stop you they could also be the only reason you're still alive. In ZWAARD you will be able to customize your sword components in hundreds of different ways allowing many different playstyles

LIVE NOW ON KICKSTARTER: kck.st/3SqJSqY
WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2251170/Zwaard/
FOLLOW ON TWITTER: https://twitter.com/Gamedev_461
